    "uen": "201001582R",
    "description": "<p>HSS ENVIRO PTE LTD was set up in 2010 to produce Liquefied Stabilized Soil (LSS). LSS is generally used as a backfilling material. It is an environmentally friendly, self-compacting and affordable material. The different challenges faced by the conventional way of backfilling – tight time frames, labour shortages, varying weather conditions can be curbed easily with LSS.</p>\n<p>We set up our plant from a plot of land located in Marina East Drive. We then need to go through a long period of intensive R&amp;D before we became fully operational. It took HSS Enviro another few more years to gain market recognition from the construction industry.</p>\n<p>Fast forward to present, some of our involvements to name a few are/were, Resorts World Sentosa, multiple MRT projects, MCE/KPE expressway, SP Cable Tunnel Projects, PUB projects, National Gallery Singapore, Jewel Changi Airport, Mandai Bird Park, just to name a few.</p>\n<p>We are proud of the fact, HSS ENVIRO PTE LTD has gained recognition as a reliable LSS supplier acknowledged by our construction industry.</p>",
